data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 5-bedroom, 3.5-bath residence offers spacious living in minutes from Lackland AFB. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an open and inviting floor plan, perfect for hosting family and friends. The modern kitchen features included high-end appliances, ample counter space, and a convenient island, making it a chef's delight. One of the standout features of this home is its eco-friendly touch. Equipped with solar panels, you'll enjoy reduced energy costs and peace of mind knowing that **designated outlets will stay powered during unexpected outages**. The primary bedroom suite is a true retreat, offering a generous walk-in closet and a spa-like ensuite bath with a soaking tub and separate shower. Four additional bedrooms provide plenty of space to spread out!
